'''Alaa Al Hejji''' ({{langx|ar|علاء آل حجي}}; born 3 December 1995) is a Saudi Arabian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Neom SC|Neom]] in the [[Saudi Professional League]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=ALAA AL HEJJI|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/alaa-hejji/419504/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=اللاعب: علاء حجي آل حجي|url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=122681}}</ref>

==Career==
On 7 March 2020, Al Hejji joined [[Al-Wehda Club (Mecca)|Al-Wehda]] on a pre-contract agreement.<ref>{{cite web |title=الوحدة يتعاقد مع حارس الأهلي ومحور وسط الخليج |url=https://ajel.sa/V2JMYc/}}</ref> He officially joined the club following the conclusion of the 2019–20 season.

On 17 July 2025, Al Hejji joined newly-promoted Saudi Pro League club [[Neom SC|Neom]].<ref>{{cite web |title=رسمياً… علاء آل حجي إلى نيوم |url=https://aawsat.com/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9-%D8%B3%D8%B9%D9%88%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A9/5165879-%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%8B%E2%80%A6-%D8%B9%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D8%A2%D9%84-%D8%AD%D8%AC%D9%8A-%D8%A5%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%86%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85}}</ref>

